<p rend="centre"> Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</p>

<p rend="book">Naradakkhadīpanī</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Pālito <pb ed="M" n="0.0008" /> yeva saddhammo,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Pālitena varena ca;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Pālite suṭṭhu yaṃ sīlaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Pālitaṃ dhamma-sundaraṃ.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Sammā <pb ed="M" n="0.0010" /> āraddhaṃ sabba-sampattīnaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Mūlaṃ hotīti daṭṭhabbaṃ.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Vīriyārabbho <pb ed="M" n="0.0011" /> bhikkhave,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Mahato atthāya saṃvattatīti.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Tasmā <pb ed="M" n="0.0012" /> vīriyameva kattabbaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Vīriyavato hi acintitaṃpi hoti.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Yathā <pb ed="M" n="0.0021" /> hi tacchakānaṃ suttaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Pamāṇaṃ hoti;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Eva metampi viññūnaṃ.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Suvijāno <pb ed="M" n="0.0024" /> bhavaṃ hoti,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Dubbijāno parābhavo;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Dhammakāmo bhavaṃ hoti,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Dhammadessī parābhavo.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Ayaṃ <pb ed="M" n="0.0026" /> dhammatāti ayaṃ sabhāvo,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Ayaṃ niyāmoti vuttaṃ hoti.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Ye <pb ed="M" n="0.0028" /> dhammā hetupabhavā,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Tesaṃ hetuṃ tathāgato.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Ratanattayaṃ <pb ed="M" n="0.0035" />, santataṃ, ahaṃ vandāmi;</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Ācariyaṃ, so ahaṃ, niccaṃ namāmi;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">‘‘Hotu sabbaṃ, maṅgalaṃ, mamaṃ sabbadhi’’.</p>

<p rend="title">Naradakkhadīpanī</p>

<p rend="centre">Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</p>

<p rend="chapter">Paṇāma</p>
</body>
